    feat(flash): [v1.0.2] add boot_storage.sh for dynamic NVMe path switching
    
    - Implement `jetpack_7.0_create_adv_boot_storage_v2` to generate the helper script.
    - Support dynamic modification of `EXTERNAL_DEVICE` in `jetson-agx-thor-devkit.conf`.
    - Use `sed --follow-symlinks` to ensure configuration link integrity is preserved.
    - Decouple parameter setup from the flash process for a safer, manual workflow.
    - Registered the new function call in `task_patch.sh`.

